      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software must be validated for structural analysis under FDA 21 CFR Part 11 requirements; version-controlled build with traceable test suite.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under ISO 9001-compliant QMS; software qualification records on file; unit and integration test suite executed at release; no open defects affecting structural solver path."
